name: Underground Hustlin CD Package! - featuring Heads Inda Clouds
description:
A collection of underground music, mostly of the Juggalo Community. Brought to you by Intriznik music. 

Heads Inda Clouds is featured on these two collections.

Volume 19 - features the song "Tick Tock" from Mike C. and Quicsand. As well as guest appearances from Snug Brim, Mars and Chamillionaire. (Promo CD. No cover art.)

Volume 20 -  is hosted by Ron Jeremy who shouts out Heads Inda Clouds on the track "Hump That". This is one of the funniest albums to ever be pressed. No Lie!

(Full Color Printing, Jewel Case, and Booklet with Pics, Credits and Ads From Intriznik.)
